<div>
    <h2>Academic Regulations</h2>

    <div>
        <h3>Academic Schedule</h3>
        <p>An academic year at IIE comprises of 2 semesters, spring semester begins in March and ends in July; fall semester begins in September and ends in January. One semester includes 20 weeks, and final examination is held in the last 2 weeks. The details illustrated in the school calendar at the beginning of each semester.</p>
    </div>

    <div>
        <h3>Duration of Study</h3>
        <p>An international student can study in IIE for a bachelor’s degree, a master’s degree, or for a non-degree program. The designated duration of study is illustrated below:</p>

        <table class="table">
            <tr>
                <th>Program</th>
                <th>Standard Duration(Years)</th>
                <th>Maximum Duration(Years)</th>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td>Bachelors Degree</td>
                <td>4</td>
